      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S ROCKY (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last five runs. Last start finished 2nd on June 7 over 340m at this track behind Armatree Pearler beaten 2.25 lengths (19.99) in a Maiden. Comes out of a hot form race last start. Sure to be about the mark. TILLY CARGO (6) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only one length (20.12) behind Batman Cargo at this track. Will give a great sight again. TIP TOP TAMMY (2) scored (20.25) last time out over 352m at Q Lakeside three-and-a-half months ago. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. TRUST A PROCESS (3) jumps at a shorter distance and still warrants respect.",
